The domain amazon.com attracted at least 615 million visitors annually by 2008.[80] Amazon attracts over 130 million customers to its US website per month by the start of 2016.[81] The company has also invested heavily on a massive amount of server capacity for its website, especially to handle the excessive traffic during the December Christmas holiday season.[82]
Results generated by Amazon's search engine are partly determined by promotional fees.[83]




