azon devices. They’ve also embraced innovative marketing strategies such as allowing customers to rate products with negative reviews as well as positive ones. This transparent rating system, paired with Amazon’s comprehensive A-to-Z guarantee, has inspired trust and loyalty among consumers.How To Save Money At AmazonSaving money at Amazon is easy, and there are a lot of ways to do it. First, you can sign up for emails from Amazon, which will sometimes include exclusive Amazon promo codes. Some of these are for flash sales, so be sure to check your email promptly! You can also look up Amazon promo codes right here at Groupon Coupons to find special savings and Amazon discounts on beauty items, groceries, books, holiday cards, electronics, power tools, and more.Entering A Promo Code On Amazon.comIf you're entering a promo code on the Amazon website, you'll add partway through checkout. Once you have your order total and are about to finalize, look for the promotional code entry to put in your code and save more.Amazon Sales & Special OffersIf you sign up for emails from Amazon, you’ll be notified immediately about sales, discounts, and special offers.Ready to get Amazon’s electronics, books, and other products out of your computer screen and into your life? Head to Groupon’s collection of Amazon coupons and discount codes to save big on products and shipping.Using Groupon CouponsGroupon Coupons offers a variety of in-store coupons, online promo codes, and other special offers and sales. When you see a coupon that can be used as a printable in-store coupon or as an online promo code, it'll look like this:Promo codes that can be used online only will typically look like this:And finally, special sales will look like this:Read moreShare these coupons    Related StoresNeiman Marcus Nordstrom Kohl's Macy's Saks OFF 5TH Sears Walmart Target Saks Fifth Avenue JCPenney Nordstrom Rack Bloomingdale's QVC Sam's Club Kmart BJ's Wholesale Club Hayneedle Woot Belk Boscov's TmartLi